sc_cat_item.description:
Apple's iPhone X isn't just bigger—it's better in every way. A 5.8-inch Retina HD display. An A11 Bionic chip with 64-bit architecture.

Key Features:

  • 5.8-inch (diagonal) all-screen OLED Multi-Touch display
  • 2436x1125-pixel resolution at 458 ppi
  • 1,000,000:1 contrast ratio (typical)
  • 625 cd/m² max brightness (typical)
  • Support for display of multiple languages and characters simultaneously
  • Fingerprint-resistant oleophobic coating
